{"tid":566664,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"英樂施會員工賑災嫖妓　香港樂施會4日收480電話取消捐款　澄清非屬會關係","createTime":"2018-02-20T06:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T09:46:23.000Z","uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a944f8f02840b62250966873eb355f19ea112a5a","tid":566664,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"英國樂施會（Oxfam）員工被揭發涉嫌在2010年海地賑災期間召妓，事件引起國際關係。香港樂施會傳訊部主管徐國偉表示，當時透過西班牙樂施會、而非英國樂施會支持海地賑災項目，但自從爆出醜聞後，香港樂施會在4日內收到480個電話要求停止捐款，預計農曆新年假期後會有更多人要求停止捐款，他呼籲市民給予時間該會改善機制。<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：英樂施會報告揭員工劣行 召妓、下載鹹片、恐嚇證人<br />\n<br />\n徐國偉今早接受商台電話訪問時回應事件，澄清本港樂施會是透過西班牙樂施會以1080萬港元支持海地救災項目，而非涉事的英國樂施會。他又指香港與英國樂施會並非屬會關係。<br />\n<br />\n徐國偉表示，自醜聞傳出後，香港樂施會4日內收到480個電話要求停止捐款，暫時未知受影響金額。他預計當農曆新年假期結束後，將會收到更多來電要求停止捐款。<span style=\"color: red;\">他擔心事件影響市民對該會的信心，以至<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">影響長遠項目的捐款</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n徐說香港樂施會現時已暫停向英國樂施會項目的捐款計劃，但已捐款而進行中的項目仍然會繼續。<br />\n<br />\n徐透露香港樂施會總裁已就事件向英國樂施會投訴並要求解釋，對方已承認錯誤及承諾會改善。另外，國際樂施會已宣布改革措施，建立所有員工的刑事資料庫。香港樂施會亦會加強內部運作，包括鼓勵舉報及加強投訴電話的內部調查機制，徐國偉呼籲公眾給予時間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180220/s00001/1519092228841\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180220%2Fs00001%2F1519092228841&d=BIV5xndJp99C8eXOj408iDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=42f4ec87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180220%2Fs00001%2F1519092228841&h=b3cca874\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180220/s00001/1519092228841</a>"},{"pid":"3ecb751be19e99739854845659105965027c4f96","tid":566664,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:50:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5360d3f7911c721a1e6910d51e44e91f5a0e65fe","tid":566664,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:56:10.000Z","msg":"割席要快"},{"pid":"01f4f8f11207f92b07019460b8ccbbad9cd07c1b","tid":566664,"uid":84619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c08f346c268e914bce131d3325f1eb98bfc6818","tid":566664,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"資助左幾年<br />\ncut 鳩晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0919bd4895d6493172fc8d5e3c652964cbbbd3fe","tid":566664,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e542a2e34420152558f111d71d80667bf8fafe","tid":566664,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bbd51388b9ff8496773001e6d2c473408f5943","tid":566664,"uid":170601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"香港分部捐的錢去非洲窮國家，英國果分部唔係去果度做野0架咩？<br />\n有得分割0架咩？"},{"pid":"211dfec8fdfe549ac68a196200addd2f350e316d","tid":566664,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:28:11.000Z","msg":"呢d仆街咁撚緊張<br />\n每個月捐撚埋份糧囉 屌你老母"},{"pid":"be45c629a4ea644c84a39ebf857b795d33af5522","tid":566664,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"從不捐錢"},{"pid":"129e3fc1f48378a87f7b81784a7f4995bff5abfb","tid":566664,"uid":84228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:36:01.000Z","msg":"割席快撚到"},{"pid":"b188db5de15421b9edcb853c108fef5b4518f299","tid":566664,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T09:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/